_diffrn_special_details          
;
When taking only strong reflections into account, indexing of the diffraction pattern is possible with a small body centered orthorhombic unit cell with a = 6.37 A, b = 12.24 A and c = 18.58. A careful examination of the reciprocal space reconstructions clearly reveals weak superstructure reflecions requiring a doubling of the a-axis, 
finally leading to a primitive orthorhombic unit cell of a = 12.7426 A (2 x a), b = 18.5776 A and c = 12.239 A (according to the standard setting in the space group Pnnm).
Since the superstructure reflections are only very weak the refinement needs a slight damping (DAMP 20) to avoid large shifts/esd ratios.
;
