_olex2_refinement_description    
;
1. Fixed Uiso
 At 1.2 times of:
  All N(H,H) groups
2. Uiso/Uaniso restraints and constraints
Uanis(I5A) = Uanis(I5B)
Uanis(I3A) = Uanis(I3B)
3. Rigid body (RIGU) restrains
 N1, C1, N2, N3, C2, N4
 with sigma for 1-2 distances of 0.004 and sigma for 1-3 distances of 0.004
4. Others
 Sof(I5A)=Sof(I3B)=0.5*(1-FVAR(2))
 Sof(I5B)=Sof(I3A)=0.5*FVAR(2)
 Fixed Sof: H1A(0.5) H1B(0.5) H4A(0.5) H4B(0.5)
5.a X=CH2 refined with riding coordinates:
 N1(H1A,H1B), N2(H2A,H2B), N4(H4A,H4B), N3(H3A,H3B)
;
